ZH: 玫瑰是一种美丽的花。
EN: Roses are beautiful flowers.
ZH: 玫瑰花有不同颜色。
EN: Roses come in different colors.
ZH: 那束玫瑰花真漂亮!
EN: That bouquet of roses is so beautiful!
ZH: 她最喜欢的花是玫瑰。
EN: Her favorite flower is the rose.
ZH: 他送了她一束红色的玫瑰。
EN: He gave her a bouquet of red roses.
ZH: 玫瑰花有甜美的气味。
EN: Roses have a sweet fragrance.
ZH: 我爱看玫瑰花开的样子。
EN: I love watching roses bloom.
ZH: 玫瑰花被称为爱情之花。
EN: Roses are known as the flower of love.
ZH: 这朵玫瑰花很漂亮，看起来很新鲜。
EN: This rose is very beautiful and looks fresh.
ZH: 我收到了一束香槟色的玫瑰花。
EN: I received a bouquet of champagne-colored roses.
ZH: 她在花园里种了许多不同种类的玫瑰。
EN: She planted many different types of roses in her garden.
ZH: 钉多少就有多少朵玫瑰。
EN: Nail as many roses as you want.
ZH: 他送给她一束粉色的玫瑰花庆祝他们的约会一周年。
EN: He gave her a bouquet of pink roses to celebrate their one-year anniversary.
ZH: 春天是玫瑰盛开的季节。
EN: Spring is the season when roses bloom.
ZH: 这座城市以生产优质的玫瑰著称。
EN: This city is famous for producing high-quality roses.
ZH: 把你的爱告诉她，就像一朵美丽的玫瑰。
EN: Tell her your love, just like a beautiful rose.
ZH: 他送给她一束蓝色的玫瑰，这是她最喜欢的颜色。
EN: He gave her a bouquet of blue roses, which is her favorite color.
ZH: 她拿起玫瑰花，轻轻地闻了一下。
EN: She picked up the rose and gently smelled it.
ZH: 我想在花园里种一些白色的玫瑰。
EN: I want to plant some white roses in the garden.
